Retail


 




Don’t be the Next Big Headline
Retailers have been a target for malicious actors since the first person clicked a purchase icon on a website in 1994. Today, payment card information is constantly being shared and processed online, making it vulnerable to theft and misuse.
With lucrative stores of personally identifiable information (PII) and payment card information(PCI), malicious actors are constantly investing in ways to skim, hack, and phish data from retailers and their customers – making strong data security essential.

Retailers struggle with implementing restrictive security solutions for fear of making the purchasing process more difficult, slower, and less convenient. This puts both customers and retailers in a very vulnerable position and leaves them open to large scale breaches.

 Authomate’s StrongPass Business suite provides retailers and customers with an easy-to-use and robust credential authentication solution. StrongPass verifies a user’s identity using multiple context aware parameters and then prevents attacks by orchestrating credentials away from where the malicious actors sit.


Benefits of StrongPass:

Bolsters customer confidence and attracts new customers
Prevents PII leakage from backend systems and mobile payment platforms
Assists meeting compliance obligations under PCI Data Security Standards (PCI DSS)
Bottom line savings by mitigating fraudulent transactions
Protection of brand and corporate reputation
Credential sharing without exposing the user and credentials to misuse or theft



