Solutions Home


 




Stronger Protection for All
Authomate’s StrongPass Business Suite is the next generation of authentication solutions that provides frontline defense for companies across all industries. It ensures:

Integrity of users’ online presence
Empowerment of users to ensure productivity in the workplace and retention among customers and end users.
Compliance and governance polices are met
Alignment between user risk profiles and security strategies
Data security is delivered cost effectively and with positive return on investment
Balance between Convenience of users and Securely delivering data

StrongPass combats credential theft, token loss, and user fatigue while helping manage security spend by securely vaulting credentials on each user’s trusted mobile device, providing a user-friendly interface and mitigates the vulnerability risks that still exist with all other point solutions.
 
 


StrongPass enables a significantly improved online experience with just a mobile device and one secure login.  Organizations and individuals finally get an authentication solution that finds the balance between strong security, user convenience, compliance mandates, and cost effectiveness.
