Authomate Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 7:39 AM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Authomate Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Authomate Inc. provides online security and authentication software solutions for consumers, professionals, and enterprises. It offers consumer products, such as StrongPass, a user login/password management service that simplifies the management of user IDs and passwords while protecting against phishing, key loggers, and man-in-the-middle attacks; and StrongBox that provides security for online documents through a document manager. The company also provides enterprise solutions that include StrongPass Enterprise, which protects company’s sensitive data; StrongBox for Enterprises that delivers security to company’s online documents; and StrongTrans for Enterprises that delivers authenticatio...
Authomate Inc. provides online security and authentication software solutions for consumers, professionals, and enterprises. It offers consumer products, such as StrongPass, a user login/password management service that simplifies the management of user IDs and passwords while protecting against phishing, key loggers, and man-in-the-middle attacks; and StrongBox that provides security for online documents through a document manager. The company also provides enterprise solutions that include StrongPass Enterprise, which protects company’s sensitive data; StrongBox for Enterprises that delivers security to company’s online documents; and StrongTrans for Enterprises that delivers authentication security to protect critical transactions. Authomate Inc. was founded in 2012 and is based in Morganville, New Jersey.
Detailed Description


