Who We Are
Established in 2012 and based in New Jersey, we have a driving goal of providing secure access to what matters most to you,
      and a passion to defeat the notion that security breaches have become inevitable. Built by a team with decades of security,
      infrastructure, defense and intelligence experience, we have collaborated to create a foundational and game changing patented authentication technology.
